"As a virtual reality researcher, I would like the ability to synchronize my recordings of a session 
together so that I can easily compare and play them at the same time"
Labels: Deliver First (High Risk/High Value)
Moscow: Must
Story Points: 18

Background: 
"I need to have the videos synchronised.  Its only after each set of videos for a given participant 
are synced that I can look through them and analyse them for points of interest.  Then after I've 
looked at all the participants I will move on to looking for patterns between them. "
